bridges and pathways

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:56.300 align:middle line:84%
between our ordinary
consciousness and transcendent

00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:58.930 align:middle line:84%
states of superconscious
awareness.

00:00:58.930 --> 00:01:02.530 align:middle line:90%


00:01:02.530 --> 00:01:05.590 align:middle line:84%
We explored in season 1
how the universe consists

00:01:05.590 --> 00:01:10.150 align:middle line:84%
of a unified field of sentient
awareness and intelligence,

00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:14.410 align:middle line:84%
or as hermeticists
say, the all is mind.

00:01:14.410 --> 00:01:17.230 align:middle line:84%
Physicist Menas
Kafatos identifies

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:22.080 align:middle line:84%
the sentient awareness as the
foundation of the universe.

00:01:22.080 --> 00:01:25.120 align:middle line:84%
It is the source of
information and energy

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:28.850 align:middle line:84%
that gets transmitted
throughout the cosmos.

00:01:28.850 --> 00:01:32.920 align:middle line:84%
But like a fish whose whole life
has been lived in the water,

00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:36.470 align:middle line:84%
we may not have awareness
of the sea of consciousness

00:01:36.470 --> 00:01:38.600 align:middle line:90%
we are swimming in.

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:41.350 align:middle line:90%
So how do we become aware?

00:01:41.350 --> 00:01:43.140 align:middle line:84%
First, we must
realize that sentience

00:01:43.140 --> 00:01:48.310 align:middle line:84%
is found at all levels, from
the subatomic to the cosmic.

00:01:48.310 --> 00:01:53.350 align:middle line:84%
This sentience is then organized
into systems of hierarchies.

00:01:53.350 --> 00:01:55.300 align:middle line:84%
On the most basic
end of the spectrum,

00:01:55.300 --> 00:01:58.450 align:middle line:84%
sentience means
something has the ability

00:01:58.450 --> 00:02:01.510 align:middle line:84%
to interact with
its environment,

00:02:01.510 --> 00:02:06.400 align:middle line:84%
receiving information and
responding to it in some way.

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:08.830 align:middle line:84%
An example of this on
the subatomic level

00:02:08.830 --> 00:02:11.680 align:middle line:84%
is how quantum particles
interact with each other

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:16.190 align:middle line:84%
through force carriers that
carry certain information.

00:02:16.190 --> 00:02:20.230 align:middle line:84%
All of this is governed by
and responsive to the laws

00:02:20.230 --> 00:02:22.060 align:middle line:90%
of physics.

00:02:22.060 --> 00:02:24.790 align:middle line:84%
As we move up the
spectrum of hierarchies

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:28.000 align:middle line:84%
to more complex
forms of sentience,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.390 align:middle line:84%
we encounter various
minerals and crystals,

00:02:31.390 --> 00:02:36.610 align:middle line:84%
then single-celled organisms,
plants, animals, humans,

00:02:36.610 --> 00:02:39.940 align:middle line:84%
planetary systems, and
beyond, all the way

00:02:39.940 --> 00:02:42.550 align:middle line:90%
to the universal mind.

00:02:42.550 --> 00:02:46.990 align:middle line:84%
The cosmos consists
of the sum total

00:02:46.990 --> 00:02:51.550 align:middle line:84%
of all these nested
systems of sentience.

00:02:51.550 --> 00:02:54.250 align:middle line:84%
This perspective of
a sentient universe

00:02:54.250 --> 00:02:57.440 align:middle line:84%
challenges that
materialist perspective

00:02:57.440 --> 00:02:59.770 align:middle line:84%
which views the capacity
for consciousness

00:02:59.770 --> 00:03:03.280 align:middle line:84%
more as an epiphenomenon
of the brain.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:06.850 align:middle line:84%
They say that the material
or physical comes first,

00:03:06.850 --> 00:03:09.910 align:middle line:84%
and then consciousness
derives from it.

00:03:09.910 --> 00:03:13.570 align:middle line:84%
Now in the hermetic view,
where the all is mind,

00:03:13.570 --> 00:03:18.130 align:middle line:84%
well, mind is primary, while
the material world is simply

00:03:18.130 --> 00:03:22.945 align:middle line:84%
one macrosystem manifested
within the one mind.

00:03:22.945 --> 00:03:25.450 align:middle line:84%
Now, before we go any
further with this,

00:03:25.450 --> 00:03:30.230 align:middle line:84%
let's distinguish the difference
between two states of mind--

00:03:30.230 --> 00:03:33.760 align:middle line:84%
namely consciousness
and awareness.

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:37.350 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is about
awakened perception.

00:03:37.350 --> 00:03:40.330 align:middle line:84%
It is the goal of
our life experience,

00:03:40.330 --> 00:03:44.020 align:middle line:84%
while awareness here is
defined as the universal field

00:03:44.020 --> 00:03:46.570 align:middle line:90%
of intelligence and sentience.

00:03:46.570 --> 00:03:50.830 align:middle line:84%
Awareness-- we can think of it
more as an inner experience.

00:03:50.830 --> 00:03:53.350 align:middle line:84%
Like when we're coming
out of a sleep state

00:03:53.350 --> 00:03:56.530 align:middle line:84%
we start to wake up, but
our eyes are still closed.

00:03:56.530 --> 00:04:00.910 align:middle line:10%
At this point, we're self
aware, recognizing, I'm here.

00:04:00.910 --> 00:04:01.930 align:middle line:90%
I'm awake.

00:04:01.930 --> 00:04:04.240 align:middle line:90%
I am.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:07.240 align:middle line:10%
This moment is
like the I am state

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:10.190 align:middle line:10%
of awareness at the top
of the Tree of Life--

00:04:10.190 --> 00:04:12.925 align:middle line:10%
that first emanation
from the source.

00:04:12.925 --> 00:04:16.930 align:middle line:90%
, it is the center of being now.

00:04:16.930 --> 00:04:19.720 align:middle line:84%
As soon as we open
our eyes, we become

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:22.360 align:middle line:84%
conscious of the things
that are outside of us--

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:26.710 align:middle line:84%
our environment and our ability
to expand and express ourselves

00:04:26.710 --> 00:04:28.450 align:middle line:90%
into the outer.

00:04:28.450 --> 00:04:31.300 align:middle line:84%
When awake, we can
take in information

00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:35.620 align:middle line:84%
from our surroundings and from
other forms of intelligence

00:04:35.620 --> 00:04:40.180 align:middle line:84%
and the various stimuli that are
coming in to us from outside.

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:42.290 align:middle line:90%
This is consciousness.

00:04:42.290 --> 00:04:46.840 align:middle line:84%
It is that more active
experience with our eyes open.

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:50.920 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is a state of
being fully awake and aware.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:53.110 align:middle line:84%
We might compare it to
the beta gamma brainwave

00:04:53.110 --> 00:04:57.610 align:middle line:84%
states that allow us to be
aware of self and others.

00:04:57.610 --> 00:05:02.300 align:middle line:84%
But awareness itself is the
foundation to consciousness.

00:05:02.300 --> 00:05:04.930 align:middle line:84%
It is more like the alpha
theta brainwave states

00:05:04.930 --> 00:05:07.910 align:middle line:90%
of inward experience.

00:05:07.910 --> 00:05:11.320 align:middle line:84%
How do we begin
optimizing our brain?

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:14.290 align:middle line:84%
Well, it begins with making
the correct connections

00:05:14.290 --> 00:05:20.170 align:middle line:84%
or bridges between our brain,
our mind, and the one mind.

00:05:20.170 --> 00:05:22.870 align:middle line:84%
When we can strengthen and
solidify these connections

00:05:22.870 --> 00:05:26.170 align:middle line:84%
by stimulating our brain
and neurological system

00:05:26.170 --> 00:05:29.080 align:middle line:84%
with the proper
vibrational energies--

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:33.070 align:middle line:84%
these can include energies such
as light, sound, touch, breath,

00:05:33.070 --> 00:05:38.080 align:middle line:84%
aromas, all tuned in to
the correct frequencies.

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:40.000 align:middle line:84%
Through this journey,
we'll explore

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:43.690 align:middle line:84%
seven bridges or connective
circuits between our brain

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:47.290 align:middle line:84%
regions and various
levels of consciousness.

00:05:47.290 --> 00:05:49.750 align:middle line:84%
The goal of this
exploration is to forge

00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:53.770 align:middle line:84%
a path that leads us from our
regular experience of life

00:05:53.770 --> 00:05:58.400 align:middle line:84%
back to the feeling of oneness
with universal consciousness.

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.930 align:middle line:84%
The first bridge on this
journey begins with our mind.

00:06:01.930 --> 00:06:03.580 align:middle line:90%
What is the mind?

00:06:03.580 --> 00:06:06.310 align:middle line:84%
And how is it connected
to consciousness

00:06:06.310 --> 00:06:09.490 align:middle line:90%
and our brain-body system?

00:06:09.490 --> 00:06:14.400 align:middle line:84%
The mind is a complex framework
of thoughts and emotions

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:17.905 align:middle line:84%
that directly interface
with the brain-body system.

00:06:17.905 --> 00:06:22.420 align:middle line:84%
But first, it connects
in and through our soul.

00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:27.760 align:middle line:84%
The primary function of the mind
is to become aware of stimulus

00:06:27.760 --> 00:06:30.640 align:middle line:84%
coming in from spirit
or from the one mind,

00:06:30.640 --> 00:06:34.780 align:middle line:84%
and then to direct our actions
according to intention.

00:06:34.780 --> 00:06:37.470 align:middle line:84%
The mind has different
levels to it,

00:06:37.470 --> 00:06:39.340 align:middle line:84%
and so to make it
easy for us here,

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:43.480 align:middle line:84%
let's just try to call them the
lower mind and the higher mind.

00:06:43.480 --> 00:06:48.280 align:middle line:84%
The lower mind is programmed
through life experiences.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:52.270 align:middle line:84%
It is influenced by our
education, our expectations,

00:06:52.270 --> 00:06:57.580 align:middle line:84%
desires, habits, belief systems,
and emotional attachments.

00:06:57.580 --> 00:06:59.360 align:middle line:84%
It forms part of
our personality,

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:04.190 align:middle line:84%
which is the mask we identify
with in our outer life.

00:07:04.190 --> 00:07:06.090 align:middle line:84%
Now, the higher mind,
on the other hand,

00:07:06.090 --> 00:07:10.160 align:middle line:84%
is influenced directly
by spirit, or true self.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.830 align:middle line:84%
It communicates to us
through subtle energies

00:07:12.830 --> 00:07:15.050 align:middle line:90%
of our inner world.

00:07:15.050 --> 00:07:19.010 align:middle line:84%
We tap into these in meditation
and through intuition

00:07:19.010 --> 00:07:22.580 align:middle line:84%
or a sense of purpose,
meaning, and potential.

00:07:22.580 --> 00:07:27.080 align:middle line:84%
Our higher mind is part of
our original patterning,

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:29.450 align:middle line:90%
our spiritual blueprint.

00:07:29.450 --> 00:07:34.310 align:middle line:84%
This blueprint contains
our purpose, our contracts,

00:07:34.310 --> 00:07:37.860 align:middle line:84%
and our whole reason
for being here.

00:07:37.860 --> 00:07:39.800 align:middle line:84%
Now, these two
levels of our mind--

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:43.070 align:middle line:84%
higher and lower--
they help us to operate

00:07:43.070 --> 00:07:45.500 align:middle line:84%
within this physical
density, and also

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:48.800 align:middle line:84%
to connect with
our eternal spirit.

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:51.320 align:middle line:10%
We can represent them
on the Tree of Life

00:07:51.320 --> 00:07:54.050 align:middle line:10%
as the lower two triads.

00:07:54.050 --> 00:07:56.210 align:middle line:10%
The physical body is
at the very bottom

00:07:56.210 --> 00:07:59.000 align:middle line:10%
of the tree, the bottom sphere.

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:03.230 align:middle line:10%
The lower mind is the
lowest of the three triads.

00:08:03.230 --> 00:08:06.590 align:middle line:10%
The higher mind is what
we call the middle triad,

00:08:06.590 --> 00:08:10.390 align:middle line:10%
while the spirit
is the upper triad.

00:08:10.390 --> 00:08:14.080 align:middle line:84%
In addition to this arrangement
on the Tree of Life,

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:17.620 align:middle line:90%
where is our mind located?

00:08:17.620 --> 00:08:20.530 align:middle line:84%
If it's on the Tree
of Life, that also

00:08:20.530 --> 00:08:26.260 align:middle line:84%
means it is in our
physical and spiritual DNA.

00:08:26.260 --> 00:08:30.410 align:middle line:84%
It's in every cell of the
body, not just the brain.

00:08:30.410 --> 00:08:32.179 align:middle line:84%
But it's not only
the physical body.

00:08:32.179 --> 00:08:36.850 align:middle line:84%
The mind extends beyond the body
and reaches out to the infinite

00:08:36.850 --> 00:08:38.275 align:middle line:90%
to touch the one mind.

00:08:38.275 --> 00:08:40.929 align:middle line:90%


00:08:40.929 --> 00:08:43.780 align:middle line:84%
Let's try to make this
more relatable, here.

00:08:43.780 --> 00:08:45.910 align:middle line:84%
A helpful analogy
for understanding

00:08:45.910 --> 00:08:50.620 align:middle line:84%
this dynamic system is that of
a radio broadcasting analogy.

00:08:50.620 --> 00:08:53.680 align:middle line:84%
Instead of a sea of
interacting waves,

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:57.400 align:middle line:84%
think now of how radio stations
are broadcasting their signals

00:08:57.400 --> 00:08:59.510 align:middle line:90%
out to the field around them.

00:08:59.510 --> 00:09:01.030 align:middle line:84%
There are many
radio stations that

00:09:01.030 --> 00:09:05.680 align:middle line:84%
can be tuned into from a
single receiver or radio plate.

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:08.170 align:middle line:84%
That's because
they each broadcast

00:09:08.170 --> 00:09:13.000 align:middle line:84%
a slightly different frequency
in the radio wave range.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:16.490 align:middle line:84%
If we're driving in our car
and listening to the radio,

00:09:16.490 --> 00:09:18.850 align:middle line:84%
we know we can always change
to a different station

00:09:18.850 --> 00:09:21.520 align:middle line:84%
if we don't like what
we're listening to.

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:24.010 align:middle line:84%
What that means is
that we're moving

00:09:24.010 --> 00:09:27.310 align:middle line:84%
through a sea of radio
signals, all being

00:09:27.310 --> 00:09:29.440 align:middle line:84%
broadcast from
different locations

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:32.100 align:middle line:90%
and at different frequencies.

00:09:32.100 --> 00:09:36.710 align:middle line:84%
In this analogy, our
car represents our body,

00:09:36.710 --> 00:09:39.900 align:middle line:84%
while the radio receiver
is like our brain,

00:09:39.900 --> 00:09:42.190 align:middle line:90%
meaning it's the hardware.

00:09:42.190 --> 00:09:44.860 align:middle line:84%
The broadcasting stations
are like the centers

00:09:44.860 --> 00:09:47.740 align:middle line:84%
of spirit awareness
that are sending out

00:09:47.740 --> 00:09:50.080 align:middle line:84%
their ripples or
waves of information

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.830 align:middle line:90%
within the mind of the all.

00:09:52.830 --> 00:09:56.070 align:middle line:84%
Individuated mind, like
our mind that we normally

00:09:56.070 --> 00:10:00.420 align:middle line:84%
associate with, is the waves
themselves, or each radio

00:10:00.420 --> 00:10:02.880 align:middle line:90%
signal being sent out.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:06.480 align:middle line:84%
Our mind thus functions as
a field of communication

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:10.170 align:middle line:84%
between the spirit and
the brain-body system.

00:10:10.170 --> 00:10:13.800 align:middle line:84%
This communication flow
can also go both ways,

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.890 align:middle line:84%
because in our case, the
body and physical world

00:10:16.890 --> 00:10:21.360 align:middle line:84%
can also send signals and
information back to the spirit,

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:24.450 align:middle line:84%
this makes the brain-body
system more of a receiver

00:10:24.450 --> 00:10:30.450 align:middle line:84%
and transducer of m rather than
a generator of consciousness.

00:10:30.450 --> 00:10:35.410 align:middle line:84%
The mind, on the other hand,
not only transmits information--

00:10:35.410 --> 00:10:38.820 align:middle line:84%
it can also analyze and
interpret those signals

00:10:38.820 --> 00:10:40.740 align:middle line:84%
and respond back
to them according

00:10:40.740 --> 00:10:43.620 align:middle line:84%
to its mental framework
or programming.

00:10:43.620 --> 00:10:48.130 align:middle line:84%
The brain receives signals from
spirit and the collective mind,

00:10:48.130 --> 00:10:51.240 align:middle line:84%
but it is our individual
mind that is processing

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:53.670 align:middle line:90%
and interpreting those signals.

00:10:53.670 --> 00:10:56.040 align:middle line:84%
While the brain is
the hardware, our mind

00:10:56.040 --> 00:10:59.310 align:middle line:84%
is like the software or
the operating system.

00:10:59.310 --> 00:11:01.300 align:middle line:84%
In order to optimize
this system,

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:04.530 align:middle line:84%
let's take a closer look
at how it functions.

00:11:04.530 --> 00:11:06.240 align:middle line:10%
It begins with a stimulus.

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:09.180 align:middle line:10%
That stimulus comes in from
spirit, which we can also

00:11:09.180 --> 00:11:11.880 align:middle line:10%
call light, love, or will.

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:13.800 align:middle line:10%
When that stimulus
enters our field,

00:11:13.800 --> 00:11:15.690 align:middle line:10%
it is registered by our senses--

00:11:15.690 --> 00:11:20.310 align:middle line:10%
either internal, intuitive
or external, physical senses.

00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:22.930 align:middle line:84%
This then triggers
the nervous system,

00:11:22.930 --> 00:11:24.570 align:middle line:90%
and it creates a feeling--

00:11:24.570 --> 00:11:27.270 align:middle line:90%
a physical body sensation.

00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:29.910 align:middle line:84%
This sensation within
the body triggers

00:11:29.910 --> 00:11:33.990 align:middle line:84%
our wants and desires, which
then leads to a thought.

00:11:33.990 --> 00:11:36.720 align:middle line:10%
And this thought
becomes an action,

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:39.240 align:middle line:10%
which is then fed
back into the cycle,

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:42.210 align:middle line:10%
creating a feedback loop.

00:11:42.210 --> 00:11:47.130 align:middle line:10%
This whole process is
the engine of the mind.

00:11:47.130 --> 00:11:50.370 align:middle line:10%
This is the operating system.

00:11:50.370 --> 00:11:52.860 align:middle line:84%
Through understanding
Kabbalah and the Tree of Life,

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:54.960 align:middle line:84%
we can better
understand this process

00:11:54.960 --> 00:11:59.140 align:middle line:84%
and recognize it as a
cycle or feedback loop.

00:11:59.140 --> 00:12:01.990 align:middle line:84%
If we're not functioning
as we would like to,

00:12:01.990 --> 00:12:06.400 align:middle line:84%
we can interrupt the cycle
and reprogram our mind

00:12:06.400 --> 00:12:09.400 align:middle line:84%
for more positive
results, interrupting

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:12.640 align:middle line:84%
negative or destructive
self-sabotaging patterns

00:12:12.640 --> 00:12:17.110 align:middle line:84%
